quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  96,1,N’usome kw’izina ry’Umuremyi wawe yaremye
  96,2,Yaremye umuntu kukimanyu c’amaraso
  96,3,"N’usome, n’Umuremyi wawe n’umugira neza cane"
  96,4,Niyo yigishije umuntu ikoresheje ikaramu
  96,5,Yigishije umuntu ibintu atari abifitiye ubumenyi
  96,6,"None s’ibi, mu vy’ukuri umuntu yama yishima"
  96,7,Akishima yuko yaronse ubutunzi
  96,8,Ntankeka ingaruka ya bose iri ku Muremyi wawe gusa
  96,9,Mbega wabonye umwe amubuza
  96,10,Umuntu mweranda ariko arasenga
  96,11,Mbega wabonye yuko ari hejuru y’uburongozi
  96,12,Canke ategeka kugira ibikorwa vyiza
  96,13,Mbega ubona gute ko yoba ari umuhakanyi w’Imana y’ukuri nugusubira inyuma
  96,14,Mbega ntabumenyi afise yuko Imana imubona
  96,15,"None s’ibi, nata reka kugira ivyo agira, twebwe tuzomukwega kumishatsi yiwe yo kuga hori hori k’umutwe wiwe"
  96,16,Aga hori hori k’umubeshi gafise ibicumuro
  96,17,N’ahamagare basoma mbike biwe bamufashe
  96,18,Natwe tuzohamagara aba Marayika bo mu muriro udahera bamuhane
  96,19,"None\ts’ibi,\tntumugamburukire,\tahubwo\tn’upfukame\tushire\tumutwe wawe hasi ube hafi cane y’Umuremyi wawe"